{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"17601c2720bfe91fef86e2af12e8d4a4e6b25447725acdc2d52d2abb8ebb6af4","slug":"index-44","location":"/roadmap/qtdata/index.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"量潮数据工作蓝图","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/roadmap/qtdata/index.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/roadmap/qtdata/index.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"index.md","url":"/index-2e300b9116128908a02b57dfadd10d11.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们的定位","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"Lc00pzvyoN"}],"identifier":"id","label":"我们的定位","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"W7RCWkOnro"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"量潮数据主要给国内外知名高校和高新科技企业提供数据处理服务和咨询。我们的订单大多是数千元到一两万、几周结项、客户对质量要求较高的订单。这种商业模式的核心难点在于保持经营效率，减少各种隐形摩擦。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"PBUkMWibFa"}],"key":"uR4TY3ZAem"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"全世界范围内的经管科研数据、其他学科数据、下游的高新科技企业的数据需求是很多的，而我们刚好卡在了大量中小企业和科研团队需要但是市场供给稀缺的市场上。理论上我们的增长空间可以是全世界，实际上我们遍布全球的客户来源已经验证了这点。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"naT4h8G2a9"}],"key":"c3fAl9odHu"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心竞争力","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"MLAaYnxyVh"}],"identifier":"id","label":"核心竞争力","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"k7jNsc8xgd"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用四个字概括是\"产教融合\"。具体来说是技术管理能力——能把复杂的科研和企业数据需求拆解为可执行的工程方案。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"yOsrypIKJz"}],"key":"MefD6vluzR"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"学术圈和高新科技企业有密集发达的社交网络，会随着客户推荐或者学术技术合作而不断带来新客户，我们的口碑也已经迈过了这个门槛。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"YngwalVOv9"}],"key":"sbiCbKwpKQ"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们的经营困难","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"dInuSLENzH"}],"identifier":"id","label":"我们的经营困难","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"JV2vLIqtP3"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在需求侧，我们需要面对巨大的市场摩擦而面临获客困难，要面对巨大的商务谈判成本，也要面对结项不顺利的风险，更要面对事后纠纷的风险。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"WuSvCGMdCB"}],"key":"rZ0qMMwDqz"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在供给侧，我们要面临快速发展的技术和落后保守的人才培养体系。我们需要的人才都需要几乎从零开始培养。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"x2LG8kqK2m"}],"key":"y6MPDVqF3T"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们的应对思路","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"OZthT2gHI2"}],"identifier":"id","label":"我们的应对思路","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"FV5b2e5gnP"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为了应对这些问题，我们逐步形成了一整套透明、开放、精细的量潮标准化体系，把所有的利益相关方都放在同一套工作语言下整合。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"nPsI8IQtcE"}],"key":"A3T2JrUY0w"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在当前这个规模化的关键阶段，核心问题是：如何应对规模化之后可能带来的文化和制度稀释？","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"MwyuAU2MWR"}],"key":"qnq88tW3t9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这条路应当通向更高的经营效率、更高的人效比、更高的杠杆率，而不应该通向虚胖的规模。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"tztVlfRkr8"}],"key":"OcATPkwMSK"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"平台化是解法","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"nw6HROu949"}],"identifier":"id","label":"平台化是解法","html_id":"id-4","implicit":true,"key":"QKUpOSAUb1"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 Vibe 工作时代，我们的机会主要是不断减少人类执行细节工作，把人类的主要精力放在人类之间的协作相关的意义构建、决策判断上。","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"qZjg3oacZ8"}],"key":"GnTnetbNB3"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由于 Vibe 时代的研发成本急剧下降，且创始人的精力得以被释放来构建复杂系统，通过平台化整个体系来提高经营效率变成了一件性价比极高的选择。","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"DsP5xRigHf"}],"key":"FzU74tsJu1"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"研发系统的目的是解放人力用来创造，而绝非取代人力。记账和算账将会变得越来越自动化，数据部门和数据工作者的职责将会越来越面向实际业务决策，观察判断项目中的隐形成本并提出调控。","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"QStmu42vMb"}],"key":"Hr7BRrUMOy"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"比技术更重要的转型，是使用技术的人转型。如果内部固步自封与当前状态岁月静好，拒绝和市场同步，或者没有正确地探索，这些都不利于发展。","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"wsBZv9Nhrp"}],"key":"I5eYDdZKko"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"过往的成功经验","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"key":"GKOQBarzql"}],"identifier":"id","label":"过往的成功经验","html_id":"id-5","implicit":true,"key":"LGmdjn8wyq"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最重要的改变是创始人从\"专制君主\"向\"立宪君主\"、公司从\"人治\"向\"法治\"转变带来的杠杆效应。放弃中心化的决策习惯，建立去中心化的、分布式的决策新习惯，是所有企业在规模化阶段都要经历的阵痛。","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"key":"kUeWXatmfp"}],"key":"k3GemllPDl"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们成体系地梳理了一系列内部制度，包括但是不限于公司代表大会制度、矩阵式组织架构、透明化经营等。我们也花了大量的时间和客户不断沟通和改善合作关系、提高合作效率。","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"key":"rAdp3ru7vm"}],"key":"YZbwU2biUe"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们过往的成功经验，是在一次一次地技术浪潮中抓住空隙钻过去，从而一轮又一轮地苟住没倒闭。保持这样的思考是最根源的动力。","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"key":"s8cBQFDv05"}],"key":"HUFPuSF1AE"}],"key":"PzksckVjOX"}],"key":"y7VhjarKvE"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}